original_title: Mike Matei Brown Bricks stream! Roger Rabbit for Famicom Disk System!
overview: This Mike Matei Live playthrough had a Brown Bricks theme to go along with Roger Rabbit for Famicom Disk System. Don't confused this game with the regular NES game by LJN, this one is the original version of Crazy Castle.
